{"tid":820284,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[翻版朱晨麗]陳法拉處女導演作獲電影節短片獎　露宿者造型嚇親路人","createTime":"2018-09-15T10:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T10:54:07.000Z","uid":12558,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9c04b0d2fd744bb2ed8e4b6da16625019816fe5a","tid":820284,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:34:41.000Z","msg":"陳法拉的處女導演作《人來人往》，獲本屆「辛丹斯電影節：香港短片比賽」選為9部得獎短片之一，早前修畢戲劇碩士課程的她，實行學以致用，獲獎相信是對她的努力一大認可。<br />\n法拉不單擔任導演，仲上陣扮演露宿者角色，卸下平日的高貴美麗造型，穿上在垃圾桶執返嚟的舊衫褲，仲唔洗頭、指甲綑黑邊，以最貼地造型訓街開工，難怪途人都認法拉唔出，見到都匆匆掩鼻走過。<br />\n<br />\n「因為沒有budget，上至編、導、演，下至梳頭、化妝都要一腳踢，很有滿足感。」法拉透露由於預算不多，很多拍攝工作都是靠朋友以及同學仗義幫忙，包括「老豆」羅樂林和小師弟吳肇軒友情客串演出，「『老豆』還為了我這個作品第一次大聲疾呼的連環爆粗，形容是他一次突破的演出，所以非常感激他們的付出」。電影其中一幕是法拉在行人天橋上扮跳樓，她不理危險親身上陣，相當搏命！<br />\n《人來人往》分別在香港和法國取景，故事以一位露宿者以及青年的接觸為主題，這部短片是法拉小試牛刀之作，她表示劇本是利用課餘時間寫成，「去年上完編劇的課程，所以想學以致用，於是便開始寫了這個劇本。」法拉指這部短片是一個嘗試，可以在過程當中學習，認識到自己的不足：「非常感謝大家俠義幫助，沒有拍攝及後期團隊的配合支持，我根本不可能獨自完成。希望下一部有多點budget啦，哈哈！」<br />\n<br />\n法拉今年二月曾到美國參加影展，而《人來人往》將會在本月23日，與其他得獎短片一同首映。她亦透露現時正創作新的劇本，不過需要兼顧忙碌的工作，她認為：「暫時做演員是自己最主要的工作，未來有機會都樂意參與幕後創作」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/183418_3c60b61edb9b4ee6a69f6f1cf0154c9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F183418_3c60b61edb9b4ee6a69f6f1cf0154c9f.png&h=fd5ea6cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/183421_1091955000765b8ac74e467ce45cd667.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F183421_1091955000765b8ac74e467ce45cd667.png&h=1d62dbbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/183424_bb561d102b999121776c11be68b17b87.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F183424_bb561d102b999121776c11be68b17b87.png&h=542aa81d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/183427_e7079a54d007ae6c3dc85a35e1d5762b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F183427_e7079a54d007ae6c3dc85a35e1d5762b.png&h=be571ee3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14c41894fb16a1221bcee8ca268857140c0307ad","tid":820284,"uid":13996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e97e36c1ddd9ee9ca8321f4cf9244b84876393f","tid":820284,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想睇"},{"pid":"9d614242bb644e2bf15273eafcdec969b3f7d910","tid":820284,"uid":36673,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:40:57.000Z","msg":"個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嬲block定嬲屌?"},{"pid":"f4db85c28b612724b808be5f3d82cb82438f4878","tid":820284,"uid":126133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T10:41:15.000Z","msg":"腳板好黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1705d815726be9f5b0fa88822540fa5dc209bb6","tid":820284,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"嘩好大犧牲"},{"pid":"87f7a0d8bce8b2edd72ee5f62ab117250c3ef583","tid":820284,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:51:09.000Z","msg":"想屌"},{"pid":"9f502e3065b40376d96c8ec5bda481cd97106496","tid":820284,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1705d815726be9f5b0fa88822540fa5dc209bb6","tid":820284,"uid":92376,"like":0